Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:06.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:10.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:23.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna be like those lying on the street in New York today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:25.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are we like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They don't agree \N-You usually seem a little slack
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are working hard today \N-Full of energy today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:34.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm working so hard together I even got a Matsumoto-style haircut
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The hair is also wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:37.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's more like Bito Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:39.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is Bito Takeshi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:42.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can Bito Takeshi and Matsumoto have the same hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the same Matsumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's obviously the same as Bito
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, then its the same, in short i'm full of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:54.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Without further delay, we bring you the latest version of the "Someone is Here" series
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada loves this one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's super happy now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:02.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He wants to watch this while eating a burger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:03.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is his side dish  \N-His absolute favorite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've kept you waiting then
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:06.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Absolute favorite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:07.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's this:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:16.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's Someone in the Third Row in the Back Seat is Occupied Prank
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:17.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:22.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it's really good, if Hamada laughs too much, his face might break open
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His face will snap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We might see it happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:32.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, after this, the pranker in the back seat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also has someone behind them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:41.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And, the machines that are so niche they have achieved zero sales
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:50.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And, when pretending to catch a big fish, up to 5 people can be pulled into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:16.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's Someone in the Third Row in the Back Seat is Occupied Prank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:22.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,About four years ago, we did a "there's someone in the back seat" prank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:20.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it was 4 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary, this one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A normal reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The target of the prank was someone sitting in the passenger seat with someone behind them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A simple setup
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed scary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The face of the pranker is too horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:46.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, there will be someone in the third row behind the person that thinks they are pranking the person in the first row
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:49.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The reverse prank is like this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the first target is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:01.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Einsetin's Inada
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is called for the "back seat is occupied" prank
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:07.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Due to being a scary-looking comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is asked to be the setter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, he quickly gets into the back seat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:21.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The target in the passenger seat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:26.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anthony, who knows all about it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My phone seems to have been left there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'll be right back. Can you give me a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. \N -Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:39.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being lured away, Inada's chance appears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tough for Anthony too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A great expression
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So creepy  \N-Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get ready to be scared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,An arguably unsettling expression
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's looking in the rearview mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Checking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After getting into position
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah I see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A great image
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:15.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A good composition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:22.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Trifecta Prank
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will he realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His focus is ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really hope he notices
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:39.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, Anthony won't pay attention to Inada
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:43.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And probably because his attention is on the front row
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He doesn't pay attention to behind him at all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His body is so far forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A stalemate occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,An endless wait
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, after 5 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:05:01.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The man in the third row also pokes his head forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's offside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Inada still fails to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both sides are waiting to move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:21.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The distance after 10 minutes begins to close
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's moved so far forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:38.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It scared Anthony too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Almost touching
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:51.01,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,886)\fs60}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:55.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, wait a sec, let me calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:57.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha80}Gross, I want to throw up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Disgusting, I want to throw up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha80}I'm exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand what's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, I need to calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah...ah... my brain has turned around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:14.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we explained the whole thing to him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:19.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Ah~ like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Typical Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the next target is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anthony must be tired too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Audrey's Kasuga
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga has a lot of patience
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.03,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's good at waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:49.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, like Inada, his focus is also ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And is completely unaware of the behind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,An interesting image
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:59.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, for this man who is known for his endurance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:06.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,30 minutes passes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Quite a while
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not easy for anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy is good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Perseverance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:14.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, little by little, the third row moves forward
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To this extent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're almost side-by-side
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Right next to him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Quite forward both of them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This reaction is too real
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A huge surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:49.21,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(717,886)}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not as much of a response as I expected
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:59.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's because of my professionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll realize if I react too much \N -I'll realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the "Oh!", I was planning to continue with Anthony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I felt something behind me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I didn't turn around because I didn't want everything to be revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected of WedDown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:18.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After testing this a few times
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:24.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We explore what happens when the person in the passenger seat is also unaware of what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:27.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Double-prank style
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:33.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the targets are these two
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A great lineup
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go. \N -Scary enough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nice expression
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go. Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It also depends on who notices first
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go. They're all here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3 offenders with different crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The crimes committed are not of the same kind at all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:19.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The total silence of a prison van
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so it continued for 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not realized yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:36.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For some reason, Sakai begins combing his hair
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, there are two of them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,For Sakai, there are two more people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Meaning unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:55.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.71,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is indeed necessary to ask what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wants to get out first
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:02.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:09.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai, who was completely baffled by the situation, gets out of the car voluntarily
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:14.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, the man behind has not yet been noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, of course, the prank is not yet over
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:26.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such a long "oooh"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A long sound
