Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No...  \N-Still in the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh eh eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why can't I open this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, what... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not good not good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm completely confused. \N -I don't know what's going on either
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.96,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,886)\fs60}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A very small mask
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:17.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's another guy back there? You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I saw both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:20.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Behind... eh, didn't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:28.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai mistakes the project for something to do with psychics
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something's gone wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the last group of targets is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,These two
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:45.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, Shizuru's Ikeda was the setter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems to be watching some kind of video
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's break time after all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is also the possibility that the back row will realize first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lilly is concentrating on watching a video of Kamaitcahi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:13.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Moriyama is concentrating on Lily
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A stalemate occurs again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although one of them knows, the other one doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It does get confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:40.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:44.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no. What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one seems to know something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:02.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no. What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this project?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is definitely some kind of prank
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Ikeda
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ikeda
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's like the Mona Lisa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A demure face
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So funny
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is wondering why the truth hasn't been revealed yet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:44.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jumped
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bounced to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:54.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was close. A dive to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Run, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is really scary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lilly saw both
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the situation of these three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:21.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:27.90,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,886)\fs70\fad(0,300)}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:23.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,"He's always been there"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait for me to calm down. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super scared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,-Lips are quivering
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Moriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on with his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:40.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, this...who...that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh... who is being pranked here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,First time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When words of joy, anger, sorrow, and sadness are coming to me like crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My mouth always twitches and doesn't stop, it's been like this since I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really, it's genetic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.09,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※After the broadcast, Moriyama's relatives contacted him and said that their family members were really like this, and he tweeted that he imagined the whole family at his funeral with quivering lips
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one is the scariest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't stop shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:02.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1300E1&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary{\r}\N You'll be scared to shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:04.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this result?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In short, it is shaking with fear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:14.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The result is that this guy is the last person to be set up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This lip is the most frightening
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's genetic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The guy in the third row was probably also scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:24.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Is there someone hiding behind me too?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He doesn't dare to trust
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:28.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe he checked at the start
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:43.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Chocolate Planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Chocolate Planet Constellation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are the Chocolate Planet Constellation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should correct him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:58.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask, what is Chocolate Planet's strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kawashima, what are our strengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Parody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feels like a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, its small props
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:16.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true. \N -The small props used in our routine are all made by me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:21.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I made this "no contact ring"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:26.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You put it on your finger to press the elevator button without having to touch it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's suitable for now\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:33.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one passed the first stage of the Good Design Award
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:33.60,note_Wed - Mid,,0,0,0,,{Good Design Award", the highest award for Japanese design, was established in 1957 and is one of the four major design awards in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you create it?\N -I did
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:40.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So this time, we bring a theory about creations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:47.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are businesses that are so focused on niche areas that they don't even sell a single piece of machinery
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:53.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, focusing on too niche areas, not a single piece of machinery sold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There must be\N  -There must be in this world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think so \N -Not even one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I actually made a very niche machine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Never seen it before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:10.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We have all had screen cover fall on the floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are times when you can't pick it up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:17.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Especially when there are no nails  \N-Especially
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The machine that solves this problem
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it falls, you press this like this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The cover is picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid  \N-No more fear. No more fear of having no nails
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:30.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It helps elementary school students
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A machine that can help elementary school students
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:36.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No fear \N  -Yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:41.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \N Matsumoto-san said "no fear", you shouldn't just reply with "Yes, yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The machine  \N-No fear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:44.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The second time it was dropped he picked it up easily
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?  \N-This needs to be considered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What's wrong? \N -You didn't use "no fear" at all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:53.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you drop it, you can't not pick it up with this "no fear"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He picked up again directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:19.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are businesses that are so focused on niche areas that they don't even sell a single piece of machinery
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:24.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, FUJI SEIKI of Fukuoka Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:30.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The rice ball salt-spreading machine: Salt-spreading Machine No. 5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's quite big
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:36.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It sprinkles salt on the surface of the rice balls on the conveyor belt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Flips it over and sprinkles it inside once too
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:36.36,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,247)}Salt injection port
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:43.10,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,200)}Salt injection port
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A machine for sprinkling salt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:50.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As it is an excellent machine that can perform precise portion adjustment in 0.01 gram units
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is sold at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:54.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,4 million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,4 million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:59.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The price is high, but it has the performance to match
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The development cost of this machine is about 100 million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,100 million? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:09.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Salt spreader developed with substantial funding
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many units have been sold?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:17.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A total of 1,336 units were sold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's already paid for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really sold a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A best seller!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:24.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, the rice balls sold in convenience stores and supermarkets
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:29.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All need to be sprinkled with a small amount of salt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:34.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are about 500 factories nationwide that make rice balls
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Almost all factories have bought this salt spreader
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:44.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An overwhelming market share of about 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is really a best seller
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:49.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All the rice balls we eat will pass through this salt sprinkler
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:53.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Factories that actually use this salt spreader
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:58.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every day we ship 20,000 rice balls to large supermarkets
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:03.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So its impossible to salt each by hand
