Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A realistic statement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:15.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this machine for salting costs 4 million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has sold more than 1300 units
