Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.97,0:29:15.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't everyone go along with being dragged into the sea by the other person
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:18.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,1 or 2 people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.52,0:29:20.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is reasonable to say that this is the limit
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.34,0:29:21.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you use two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.81,0:29:22.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.81,0:29:25.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be fun if we could drag more people into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.11,0:29:26.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no... \N -I've always had this in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.73,0:29:29.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know, is it possible to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.74,0:29:31.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why I brought this theory.  \N-I see
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.82,0:29:33.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's witness it together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:42.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you act as if you are about to be dragged into the sea when a big fish is hooked, you can pull up to 5 people into the water with you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.29,0:29:44.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.93,0:29:47.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what happens when you catch a big fish?\N  -That's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.43,0:29:49.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shouting "no good, no good" and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.68,0:29:50.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There should be someone to come and help
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.95,0:29:53.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.41,0:29:57.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the whole group of people dragged into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.24,0:29:58.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,See how many people they can pull in with them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.78,0:30:00.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Up to 5 people?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.15,0:30:01.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is 5 people possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.58,0:30:03.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying, "No, I'm going to fall..."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.46,0:30:05.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then falling in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.76,0:30:08.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd surely be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.16,0:30:10.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It feels like something will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.13,0:30:11.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It feels like something will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.92,0:30:23.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you act as if you are about to be dragged into the sea when a big fish is hooked, you can pull up to 5 people into the water with you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.24,0:30:31.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, the stage for verification was on a boat that departed on the tide of the Miura Peninsula in Kanagawa Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.65,0:30:38.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three comedians are tasked with dragging people into the sea with them
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.14,0:30:46.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And gave fake program announcements to their close juniors stating "they can't go home without catching sailfish"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.32,0:30:49.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Under the guise of this, they will attempt to take people into the sea with them
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.92,0:30:52.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.20,0:30:53.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you--Hello, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.72,0:30:55.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here he is, Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.67,0:30:56.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Panther's Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.17,0:31:00.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I believe you are usually the one who gets pranked\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.20,0:31:02.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm super happy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.24,0:31:04.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really want to be the party responsible for pranking
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.47,0:31:07.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For physical strength, I absolutely won't lose in terms of my waist and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:08.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, I used to play soccer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.85,0:31:10.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was a midfielder
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.35,0:31:12.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The attacking strikers were flattened by me in one fell swoop
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.85,0:31:14.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'll definitely drag all the people down cleanly
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.11,0:31:24.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is true that the focus is on the physical strength
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.08,0:31:30.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Ogata will use his centripetal force to take down these juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:31.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,They look the type to be beaten easily
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:34.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are these guys trustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.07,0:31:35.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The relationship of trust is very strong
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.24,0:31:40.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anyway, they're gentle guys, and I think they're going to come running to my rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.65,0:31:47.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can he successfully drag people down by exploiting his seniority?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.14,0:31:48.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The choice of people is important
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.55,0:31:50.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Ogata-gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.99,0:31:51.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you——
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:56.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first thing is to make a decent opening
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.03,0:31:58.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Any tips? Tips for bringing in the fish
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:01.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When hooked, it creates a lot of tension
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.36,0:32:02.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you all need to focus your strength together...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.32,0:32:11.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this way, the captain subliminally plants the idea of all banding together
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.60,0:32:15.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the day of the storm, we set sail for our mission base
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.65,0:32:18.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok ok let's go \N -You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.85,0:32:19.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.62,0:32:23.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you fall into the sea in this condition, it is really dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.25,0:32:25.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we have to help each other
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.00,0:32:27.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.22,0:32:29.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Remember to shout "HIT" when you catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.76,0:32:36.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Under the captain's command, the group started fishing for sailfish without any suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.23,0:32:38.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,HIT
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.80,0:32:40.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be a sailfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.30,0:32:41.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.30,0:32:42.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it. I can't believe it. It's heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.51,0:32:49.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, Ogata establishes the rule that all members must gather after "HIT"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.98,0:32:51.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's gone
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.92,0:32:52.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.92,0:32:54.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.81,0:32:58.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, Ogata gets to work
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.96,0:33:01.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, this is in the, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.03,0:33:04.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:05.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sailfish. Sailfish hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:10.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A one-handed grip on a pre-designed weighted fishing rod
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.67,0:33:10.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It feels right
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.19,0:33:14.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is where the sailfish show begins with all its might
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.24,0:33:14.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pull it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.57,0:33:16.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts. It hurts. Hold me fast
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.71,0:33:18.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on, it hurts, it hurts
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.01,0:33:25.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They can't let the sailfish take the boss away, so they do their best to protect Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.48,0:33:22.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.65,0:33:25.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But five people in this state
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.75,0:33:26.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.62,0:33:27.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.99,0:33:27.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.18,0:33:29.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dangerous, dangerous, really dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:31.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.25,0:33:30.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,All the power is at the front
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.56,0:33:31.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So unreasonable
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.73,0:33:33.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's too unreasonable...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.97,0:33:35.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He simply wants to jump, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.43,0:33:36.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not reasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.91,0:33:43.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata tries the strategy of taking himself and the rod toward the surface of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.40,0:33:43.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's gone mad
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.96,0:33:50.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The body is tilted more than the fishing rod, creating such an amazing image
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.62,0:33:55.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, it is worthy of a group of fools led by Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.68,0:33:59.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With no sign of doubt, they assist with all their might
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.28,0:34:02.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Won't Ogata go down first?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.12,0:34:05.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, it was a stalemate for 2 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.79,0:34:08.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of location shoot is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.69,0:34:11.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.65,0:34:19.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pulled back by his group, the mission is declared a failure
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.16,0:34:21.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.94,0:34:24.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you take it easy? The fish is off the hook
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.44,0:34:30.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Be gentle and supportive"... like an idiot's lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.35,0:34:33.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was really dangerous just now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.88,0:34:36.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Truly protected him
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.98,0:34:37.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They were stronger and protected me more than I expected
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.22,0:34:39.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who made the most effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.32,0:34:40.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.56,0:34:41.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.09,0:34:45.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He had such a tight grasp on me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.93,0:34:48.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's as strong as an ox
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.77,0:34:53.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fact they went this far to save me makes me happy, but also a little angry
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.56,0:34:57.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, he understands that dragging people into the sea is not a simple matter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.81,0:35:00.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One more time... can you give me one more chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:01.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.58,0:35:05.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata starts his 2nd challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.93,0:35:08.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Elsewhere, the 2nd challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.34,0:35:13.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,TKO Kimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.86,0:35:16.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Centripetal force is indisputable
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.13,0:35:18.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am very confident
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.07,0:35:21.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kimoto, who is known for being strict with his juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.04,0:35:27.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will use a battle plan that uses the fear of seniors as a weapon to drag people down
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.87,0:35:30.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're gonna catch today!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.55,0:35:31.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.44,0:35:35.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This group begins fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.68,0:35:37.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,HIT——
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.92,0:35:42.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In order not to arouse suspicion they first carry out the normal fishing process
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.28,0:35:42.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Caught a squid
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.75,0:35:44.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.14,0:35:48.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kimoto launches the real challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.34,0:35:48.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The opening point is very well chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.89,0:35:49.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoo-hoo! Hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.59,0:35:53.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.46,0:35:54.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very large
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.33,0:35:55.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.06,0:35:57.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point is good
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.48,0:35:58.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Compared with Ogata's group
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.04,0:36:04.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Kimoto group's willingness to gather towards their leaders is significantly lower
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.00,0:36:02.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't come at all
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:06.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:09.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What should be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.71,0:36:10.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.20,0:36:16.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even with a personal distress call, the rate of gathering is still sporadic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.73,0:36:20.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The force of support is also noticeably weak
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.08,0:36:23.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The result:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.10,0:36:27.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tugging at people
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.85,0:36:30.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He uses his own initiative
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.27,0:36:30.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Had to use this trick
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.83,0:36:32.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't do it myself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:35.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Help me a little bit. Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.35,0:36:39.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is forced to pull his juniors himself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.06,0:36:42.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.58,0:36:44.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.01,0:36:44.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.44,0:36:51.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Launching a final sprint with a one-handed grip that is unimaginable for catching a sailfish
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.42,0:36:54.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.42,0:36:51.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is so weird
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.42,0:36:53.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,One hand is also too strange
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.07,0:37:07.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not good enough
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.04,0:37:09.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You don't see this very often
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.04,0:37:11.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not great
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.21,0:37:13.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Shinomiya fell down
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.60,0:37:12.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shinomiya is the only one dragged into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.18,0:37:17.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kimoto could not hide his dissatisfaction with the dismal result
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.78,0:37:17.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's so dismal
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.16,0:37:20.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.42,0:37:23.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why did you let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.55,0:37:24.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.35,0:37:25.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.56,0:37:26.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.25,0:37:30.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On board the ship, a lecture begins
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.17,0:37:32.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.85,0:37:35.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, the last challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.77,0:37:39.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.13,0:37:40.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Alco & Peace's Hirako
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.10,0:37:45.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My 182 cm 97 kg physique is not for nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.07,0:37:49.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Played for Tohoku as a football player in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.78,0:37:53.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tackling, pushing, squeezing, in short, trying to slow down the opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.88,0:37:56.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This type of movement is necessary for this
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.99,0:38:02.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the max number of people that can be brought is 5
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:04.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the goal is certainly 5
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.77,0:38:08.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5 targets including his partner Sakai
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.04,0:38:11.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hirako will attempt to drag all the people down with his own power
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.10,0:38:15.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What you catch is not a fish, but your own weak heart
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.37,0:38:17.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes \N-Understood
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.47,0:38:19.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't really buy it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.57,0:38:21.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The challenge starts
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:23.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty cold
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.85,0:38:24.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah HIT HIT HIT HIT HIT HIT
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.88,0:38:26.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, it's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:28.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So heavy, so heavy, so heavy, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:29.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Support!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.42,0:38:33.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both sides of the waist. Come here. Come here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.16,0:38:34.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,1 here, 1 here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.33,0:38:38.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait, it's really heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.33,0:38:39.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait. It's really heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:42.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.10,0:38:44.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.80,0:38:46.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not the legs, hold the waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.10,0:38:49.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reel it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.51,0:38:51.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.07,0:38:52.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The legs are dangerous, my waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.21,0:38:55.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true you'd ask "why aren't you reeling it in?"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.28,0:38:57.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.58,0:39:03.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite being shouted at, Hirako will never reel it in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.32,0:39:06.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd make you angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.42,0:39:06.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not the feet, not the feet, but the waist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.37,0:39:10.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Aiming to pull down 5 people on the first try
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:15.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Carefully assigning each person's position while figuring out the best formation
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.53,0:39:16.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why don't you reel it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.53,0:39:18.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.37,0:39:18.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should reel it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.17,0:39:20.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, the line will break ... so heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.20,0:39:21.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reel it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.17,0:39:22.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can this really be reeled in?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.84,0:39:24.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can, it can
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.97,0:39:26.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry up and reel it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.44,0:39:27.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please reel it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.10,0:39:32.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the other side, Ogata didn't even make it into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.75,0:39:35.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.10,0:39:36.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.92,0:39:37.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks like a tuna documentary
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.69,0:39:39.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because you are too strong
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.06,0:39:40.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.29,0:39:42.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Be more gentle next time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.43,0:39:43.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.80,0:39:49.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He uses an inexplicable reason to assign the strong enemy to the further location
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.67,0:39:53.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, before Nedate's arrival, he uses a lightning-fast operation
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.86,0:39:57.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Aiming to pull down 4 people at the same time as the maximum
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.18,0:40:00.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.04,0:40:01.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate is excluded
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.41,0:40:03.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.48,0:40:04.03,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good acting skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.65,0:40:06.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.98,0:40:07.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, the best performance
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.15,0:40:07.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hooked - HIT !
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.62,0:40:09.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,While Nedate is...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.18,0:40:12.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.72,0:40:14.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.23,0:40:14.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The battle plan works as Nedate's arrival is delayed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.01,0:40:16.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.56,0:40:17.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.89,0:40:20.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One by one, one by one, one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.50,0:40:20.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,After approaching
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.93,0:40:24.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.15,0:40:22.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.57,0:40:29.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.27,0:40:41.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would like to see it again
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.24,0:40:45.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fell into the sea at the same time as the enemy Nedate arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.59,0:40:45.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He could have got three
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.15,0:40:46.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He tried his best though
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.61,0:40:48.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With this judgment, two people were successfully pulled down
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.06,0:40:49.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nedate downed!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.69,0:40:51.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.96,0:40:53.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super dangerous. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.63,0:40:57.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the Kimoto Army is...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.06,0:40:58.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Try again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.73,0:40:58.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.00,0:41:01.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Same as in your live performances
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.57,0:41:04.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the place where you should be rushing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.07,0:41:06.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As soon as something went wrong you retreated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.84,0:41:07.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already lecturing about other things
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.48,0:41:08.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.  \N-This is the key moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.95,0:41:09.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's... \N -Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.57,0:41:15.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bringing lecturing to a level that has nothing to do with fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.18,0:41:18.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So unhappy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.93,0:41:20.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the customary Kimoto lecture is well and truly over
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:22.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.19,0:41:24.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No energy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.46,0:41:25.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd definitely be like this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.49,0:41:27.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd challenge begins
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.43,0:41:31.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.73,0:41:33.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because the atmosphere is not very good now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.30,0:41:36.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here it comes-
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.04,0:41:37.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,HIT
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.11,0:41:39.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already saying the atmosphere is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.21,0:41:39.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.89,0:41:44.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lecture had an effect
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.32,0:41:48.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Kimoto army come to support more actively than the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.14,0:41:51.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.12,0:41:51.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Little tighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.16,0:41:57.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please let go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.26,0:42:03.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The youngest junior, Melody Kobayashi, tries to remove his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.24,0:42:05.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Please let go" was very clear
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.45,0:42:07.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.30,0:42:17.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shinomiya again?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.49,0:42:23.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just like earlier, he ends up taking only Shinomiya with him
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.79,0:42:26.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Melody  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.52,0:42:32.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Melody, you just said "please let go", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.23,0:42:32.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.50,0:42:34.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kimoto's group is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.83,0:42:36.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's already the worst atmosphere ever
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.67,0:42:38.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This fishing trip is not fun at all
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.48,0:42:41.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kimoto and I hosted a radio program together
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.58,0:42:45.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I feel like I really shouldn't listen to his advice from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.75,0:42:53.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Back to Hirako, who's been in a stalemate for 7 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.75,0:42:54.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.75,0:42:56.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.12,0:42:57.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Make a wall, make a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.52,0:42:59.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here I am... make a wall in my place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.69,0:42:59.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? A wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.74,0:43:04.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Guiding them to the front with enigmatic instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.00,0:43:09.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He successfully distributes everyone equally around him
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.77,0:43:13.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Hirako!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.27,0:43:20.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, with everyone in place
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.84,0:43:21.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's so irritating, this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.08,0:43:22.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.21,0:43:23.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.51,0:43:24.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Working so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.48,0:43:24.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So when Hirako decides to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.08,0:43:29.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Move your foot away!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.32,0:43:33.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My feet are dangling!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.06,0:43:37.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then after 10 minutes of struggling with the false sailfish
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.24,0:43:39.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The moment has finally come
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.30,0:43:42.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Move your feet away. Move your feet away
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.60,0:43:43.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Move your feet away
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.04,0:43:52.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last two fell down!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.77,0:43:58.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.63,0:44:02.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.73,0:44:05.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was really an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.90,0:44:09.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.34,0:44:12.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.45,0:44:14.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.45,0:44:15.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.61,0:44:19.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, he acheved the desired goal and successfully dragged all five people into the sea together
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.63,0:44:20.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.93,0:44:22.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brilliantly, he validates the theory
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.22,0:44:23.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hirako!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.49,0:44:27.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the other side, Ogata, refusing to give up, continues
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.36,0:44:33.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fighting with a style beyond imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.99,0:44:40.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has become another competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.39,0:44:42.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.50,0:44:47.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.49,0:44:59.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not the main idea, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.24,0:45:03.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who wants to see it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.57,0:45:05.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has become tasteless
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.72,0:45:13.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1300E1&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary{\r}\N Hirako achieved success
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.02,0:45:17.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Sure enough, pulling down five people is a wonderful scene, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.92,0:45:18.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.80,0:45:23.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very moving to see it finally happen, just like catching a fish
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.76,0:45:25.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They didn't catch them, just let them go
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.50,0:45:29.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last two people naturally fell down
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.68,0:45:30.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.65,0:45:33.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The posture was very natural, just like a crane machine
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.07,0:45:35.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was very interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.28,0:45:37.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.25,0:45:39.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next time see if it can be done with a bungee jump
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.45,0:45:42.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a dangerous idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.39,0:45:43.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a one-person thing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.01,0:45:45.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only those who take the lead will be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.98,0:45:48.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have them hold on to them would be fun, right?
